window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p></p><p><b>Three years ago, Jacob Price walked away.</b></p><p>After a whirlwind steamy affair, my father's best friend broke my heart.</p><p>He told me things were too complicated. Messy. Wrong. That we could never be together.</p><p>I knew he loved me, but the fear of ruining our family was too great. With too much at stake, he sacrificed our hearts and ended it.</p><p>Now, he's back, and he still wants me. He still loves me.</p><p>But now, I'm engaged to another man.</p><p>From Q.B Tyler, author of <i>Love Unexpected,</i> comes an all-new age-gap forbidden romance.</p><p></p>"; 
